body:
`Seagull` doesn't want `stream` APIs and need to call docker remote API when user requests. Because the `stats` API changes after v1.19 which refers to the comments about. I change the API call with the `stream` parameter and it works well for me.

![screen shot 2016-08-28 at 00 33 43](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/2715000/18028712/285b1cee-6cb8-11e6-847d-478635c486f8.png)

@llqzwh @myml @rjorgenson You can `docker pull tobegit3hub/seagull` to update the `Seagull` image and this should be fixed. Thanks for reporting ❤️
